{"id":98498,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/08/诗和海不平/","date":"2010-08-14T23:31:58Z","modified":"2010-08-14T23:31:58Z","title":"诗和海不平","content":"<div>\n<p> </p>\n<h3>怀远人 </h3>\n<div align=\"center\"><span>作者:海不平</span></div>\n<div align=\"center\"></div>\n<div align=\"center\"><span>标签： <a href=\"http://tag.blog.sohu.com/%D4%AD%B4%B4/\">原创</a>  <a href=\"http://tag.blog.sohu.com/%CA%AB%B4%CA/\">诗词</a>  <a href=\"http://tag.blog.sohu.com/%CA%AB/\">诗</a>  </span><span>分类： <a href=\"http://haibupin.blog.sohu.com/entry/5527772/\">傲咏乡关(2006~2007)</a> </span><span>2010-08-12 12:18</span></div>\n<p align=\"center\"><span><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://1822.img.pp.sohu.com.cn/images/blog/2010/8/11/20/16/12b145ac464g214.jpg\" /></span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><span>怀远人<span></span></span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><span>提笔难书诗两行，窗前惟见月如霜。<span></span></span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><span>念伊数载无音信，苦我相思一夜长。</span></p>\n<div>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;-</div>\n<div align=\"center\">一木配诗</div>\n<div align=\"center\">\n<div>夫婿出征万里遥,<br />玉人骨立又形销.<br />管城在手悲难抑,<br />镇纸失踪字易淆.<br />书到边关一片墨,<br />梦回暖被百般娇.<br />不平惟有羞如海:<br />夜觑孤嫠上树梢.<br /><img alt=\"微笑\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://js3.pp.sohu.com.cn/ppp/images/emotion/base/smile.gif\" /> <img alt=\"偷笑\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://js3.pp.sohu.com.cn/ppp/images/emotion/base/titter.gif\" /> <img alt=\"大笑\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://js3.pp.sohu.com.cn/ppp/images/emotion/base/spit.gif\" /></div>\n<div>\n<h3>发布者 <a href=\"http://d-ym119.blog.sohu.com/\">丁一木</a> <a href=\"http://d-ym119.blog.sohu.com/rss\" name=\"onlineIcon\" rel=\"liwen119120@sohu.com;丁一木\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"12\" src=\"http://images.sohu.com/cs/sohuim/em/user_on_1_0000.gif\" /></a>(http://d-ym119.blog.sohu.com/) <br />2010-08-13 14:57 </h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>“要翻墙，<a href=\"http://bieyouyongxin.info\" target=\"_blank\">用赛风”</a>.</p>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[8800]}